<BlogLayout
  title="Apple Silicon GPU Monitoring: What macOS Doesn't Tell You"
  description="Activity Monitor barely scratches the surface of Apple Silicon GPU metrics. Here's how to get real GPU data from your M1, M2, M3, or M4 Mac."
  date="2025-10-10"
  readingTime="3 min read"
